## Description {#details}

Describes how to get a value element.

If the value is a vector then it also provides the index to extract it from.

Definition at line 249 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/transforms/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/legality-h">Legality.h</a>.
